Next up the cardinal directions.

00:01:18.735 --> 00:01:22.905
These are like the cool intermediate
stops between the main directions.

00:01:23.295 --> 00:01:28.995
We have Northeast and E, which is
naturally between north and east.

00:01:29.414 --> 00:01:33.890
Then there's Northwest and W
nestled between North and West.

00:01:34.539 --> 00:01:40.330
For the southern side, we have southeast
SE chilling between south and east,

00:01:40.780 --> 00:01:46.479
and finally southwest sw comfortably
positioned between south and west.

00:01:46.899 --> 00:01:49.479
It's like a compass, but for your brain.

00:01:49.929 --> 00:01:51.460
Let's talk about turning.

00:01:51.625 --> 00:01:55.955
This is where most friends get confused,
but it's simpler than you think.

00:01:56.640 --> 00:02:00.240
For left right turns unless
they specify something else.

00:02:00.720 --> 00:02:05.430
A turn where the left or right
always means a crisp, 90 degree turn.

00:02:05.820 --> 00:02:10.170
For instance, if you are facing north
and you take a right turn, you'll be

00:02:10.170 --> 00:02:13.020
facing east ready to catch some sunrise.

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:17.550
If you turn left, you'll be facing
west, heading towards the sunset.

00:02:17.910 --> 00:02:18.750
Easy peasy.

00:02:19.110 --> 00:02:23.730
Then we have clockwise or
anti-clockwise or counterclockwise

00:02:23.730 --> 00:02:25.290
for our international friends.

00:02:25.720 --> 00:02:28.420
These terms are all about
rotational movement.

00:02:28.600 --> 00:02:32.650
Like a Bollywood dance move
Clockwise is when you move in the

00:02:32.650 --> 00:02:37.360
same direction as the hands of your
old wall clock and anti-clockwise.

00:02:37.570 --> 00:02:41.710
That's when you go in the exact
opposite direction of those clock hands.

00:02:42.100 --> 00:02:46.030
Sometimes turns are given
in degrees like 45 degrees.

00:02:46.220 --> 00:02:49.790
1 35 degrees or a full 180 degrees.

00:02:50.239 --> 00:02:52.820
A 180 degree turn is super important.

00:02:53.030 --> 00:02:56.030
It means you've completely
reversed your direction.

00:02:56.390 --> 00:03:01.579
It's like doing an about turn in the
army parade and finally, distance.

00:03:01.910 --> 00:03:04.070
