and the shortest distance from zero

00:09:51.730 --> 00:09:53.980
zero using our good old OUS theorem.

00:09:55.344 --> 00:09:58.015
Then there's tracking net displacement.

00:09:58.344 --> 00:10:02.454
This is for the more advanced
friends, very efficient for

00:10:02.454 --> 00:10:04.735
